               <title>PRINCIPAL DISPLAY PANEL</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Rx Only</content>
                  </paragraph>
                  <paragraph>Reserved for Professional Recommendation</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>All prescriptions using this product shall be pursuant to state statutes as applicable. This is not an Orange Book product. This product may be administered only under a physician's supervision. There are no implied or explicit claims on therapeutic equivalence.</paragraph>
